Description:
Modern, Private and Well Located.
Nestled away off a quiet street in the popular Hunt Club estate, Cranbourne East, arises an amazing opportunity to purchase a beautiful family sized home, perfect for the growing family or savvy investor who's looking to get their foot into the property market.
On offer are four spacious bedrooms, two main living areas, a remote double garage and a decked pergola perfect for year round entertaining.
Upon entrance is the master bedroom, walk in robe and large en-suite with double vanity and over-sized shower, while the remaining three bedrooms at the rear of the home have their own built in robes and shared bathroom.
As you walk through, the main living area connects with the modern kitchen which includes quality stainless steel appliances, a dishwasher, stone bench tops and a long island bench providing plenty of space.
Some of the features of this home include ducted heating, split system heating/cooling, downlights throughout, two living zones and rear garage access to the backyard.
This property is in a fantastic location with many popular amenities on your door step. The Hunt Club Village Shopping Centre, Casey RACE Aquatic Centre, Casey Fields Sporting Facilities, Casey Grammar, Cranbourne East Secondary and St Thomas Primary School are all only a short walk away. Along with multiple bus stops in the estate, there are numerous parks and walking/bicycle paths nearby.
This home is sure to impress!
Call now to book your own private inspection.

Description:
When Size Matters
Contemporary in its styling, this quality built home immediately impresses with its vastness.
A touchpad pin-secured front door begins your journey into this 4 bedroom, two separate living zoned home. Upon entry an impressive hallway brings you past the extra-large master bedroom and into your first living zone.
The heart of the home is definitely the second living zone with the open plan meals kitchen with upgraded stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and multiple and clever storage facilities.
Completing the home are; double car garage, ducted heating and evaporative cooling.
Premium location in the Hunt Club with both the Cranbourne East Primary and Secondary Schools only a kilometre away, surrounded by parks, and a host of Casey's best sporting and shopping facilities, this home is brimming with both obvious and salient advantages.
With education, lifestyle, health, recreation, shopping, medical, and transportation hubs nearby
this terrific opportunity will be gone in a flash!.
This property is available for private inspection most days. Just send us an email enquiry and we will automatically respond with the available open times.
To ensure there is enough demand to inspect the property, please advise us of your wish to attend by simply following these instructions.
- Book inspection
- Select a date and time based on the options displayed
- Enter your details
- Select 'register inspection time'
You're finished! We'll keep you updated if anything changes, but otherwise we look forward to meeting you at our Hodges Open for Inspection.
**Photo ID required at ALL inspections.

Description:
A GRAND ENTERTAINER!
Located in the prestigious and tightly held Cascades on Clyde estate sits this impeccable family home situated on a 658m2 block, this home ticks all the boxes and more!
A top tier home with an array of separate living zones, huge elegant outdoor entertaining area, this exquisite residence is extremely versatile and is sure to accommodate everyone's needs.
This gorgeous 4 bedroom plus study home comes complete with a large scale master bedroom equipped with walk in robes and a full ensuite including dual vanities, spa bath and an oversized shower space!
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 600mm range hood, 5-burner gas cook top, caesar stone bench tops, glass splash back, ample overhead storage and bench space, not to mention loads of pantry space. All of this overlooking your separate meals zone!
Not only is this home fitted out with top quality fixtures and fittings it also presents a grand capacity to accommodate even the largest of families, this is truly an entertainers delight with multiple living zones on offer!
Added features include: ducted heating, neutral tones throughout, manicured gardens, internal access to your double lock up garage, exposed aggregate drive way plus 16 solar panels!
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class- A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just seconds away from the Selanda rise and hunt Club village shopping centres.
From front to back this home was completed with an exceptional eye for detail and will be the perfect residence for those that expect nothing but the best!

This custom designed family home is located within the prestigious Hunt Club Estate and within walking distance to schools, parks, supermarkets and public transport at your door step and only a 5 minute drive to Cranbourne train station, Casey Race, Casey Fields, Selandra Rise Shopping Centre and The Hunt Club shopping centre is this well designed 4 bedroom family home.

- Walk-in pantry and separate walk-in linen
- 900mm European appliances in the kitchen with Bosch dishwasher
- Waterfall stone island bench with mirror splashback

3 living zones plus huge outdoor entertaining area
If you love to entertain family and friends THIS IS THE ONE FOR YOU! Located in the well sought-after Hunt Club estate this fantastic property sits on approx. 576m2 and features stacks of extras. You will be impressed by the functional floorplan boasting THREE living zones, a separate home salon/ office if you like to work from home and to top it off a fantastic entertainer's area outside!
Comprising of:
- HUGE Master suite featuring its own en-suite plus a large walk in robe.
- Two more spacious bedrooms both with BIRs.
- Well-equipped kitchen including quality stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, gas cooktop, island bench with breakfast bar and plenty of cupboard space.
- THREE separate living areas to enjoy – a formal lounge at the front, an open plan family room at the rear and a MONSTER rumpus/ entertaining room with bifold doors opening up to the outdoor area

Description:
UNDER CONTRACT/ UNDER OFFER!
CRANBOURNE EAST: If you are looking to buy a great family home in a fabulous location then 3 Houndsforth Street needs to be seen to be appreciated!
With a functional, free flowing floor plan the property itself features 3 generous bedrooms plus study that could be used a 4th bedroom if required. The huge size master bedroom offers a WIR, FES and complete with bay-window. The other of the bedrooms all have BIR and nearby to the family bathroom with separate spa bath and shower facilities.
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and is finished with a plenty of cupboard space, large bench space, tiled splash back, S/S appliances including 900 freestanding SMEG oven & gas cook top, rangehood and dishwasher.
Take advantage of the 2 separate living zones making year-round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good movie or a book with the front living area, carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in the family zone or grab a seat around the kitchen table with the family in the dining area.
Added internal extras are gas ducted heating, s/s cooling, a mix of tiles and carpet and neutral tones throughout.
Step outside and be greeted by a sensational street scape offering a modern facade and landscaping. A wide lengthy concrete driveway leads to the remote double garage with rear access suitable for extra car, boats and trailers. The key feature of this already great family home must be the massive enclosed pergola/ sunroom that is perfect for all round use complete with full length windows and rear sliding door. The backyard is perfect for the entire family and pets with low maintenance landscaping including artificial turf and finished off with undercover BBQ area and a large garden shed/ workshop.
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate ( stop only a few doors down) making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and the vendor's expectations. You can view with confidence that the vendors will sell within the range with favourable terms and conditions.
Our floor plans are for representational purposes only and should be used as such. We accept no liability for the accuracy or details contained in our floor plans.

Description:
Perfect in Parks Edge - two living zones
Found nestled on approximately 400m2, this four bedroom family favorite boasts a low maintenance lifestyle with all amenities at your fingertips. Situated in Parks Edge in Cranbourne East in a family friendly & quiet location, the home oozes character and practical living at its best and will surely be fantastic first home or tidy investment property to add to the portfolio.
A summary of features include:
- An elegant master suite including double built in robes and an en-suite with double vanity and oversized shower.
- Three more stunning bedrooms all with BIR's.
- Impressive and well equipped kitchen with 900mm gas oven, stone benches, dishwasher, walk in pantry and breakfast bar.
- Plenty of flexible living space - a separate formal lounge plus an open plan living area at the rear.
- Undercover decked alfresco with timber feature wall and café blinds – perfect for those who entertain.
- A large backyard with plenty of room for the kids.
- Double garage with internal access.
- EXTRAS INCLUDE: ducted heating, split system cooling, a decked portico entrance, landscaped gardens, downlights throughout plus LOADS more.
All this is found close to several schools including Cranbourne East primary and Secondary schools, shopping complexes such as Shopping on Clyde and on the doorstep of all facilities Cranbourne and Berwick have to offer. Casey fields recreationally facility is also conveniently located at the end of the street –never be late to your kids footy training again! To find out more or to make this home yours please don't hesitate to meet us at the next open for inspection.
